Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After stealing one of \N the guns and some bullets... {Maybe "along with" in place of "and"? - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:15.33,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...Mista calmly loaded the cylinder \N amidst the ensuing gunfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:22.13,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...then pulled the trigger as calmly \N as a nurse inserting a needle into a patient's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.09,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He pointed the gun at the three men's faces \N and fired four perfect shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.51,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Of course, this was the first time \N he had ever killed someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.10,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...but he felt no hesitation or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:39.48,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,During this hopeless situation, \N Mista steeled himself and carved a path through the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.91,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Eat lead! {Copied from episode 7}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.16,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The guy driving must be \N the owner of the truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.71,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.08,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...his right leg is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.96,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning on killing you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.34,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,O-Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.85,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Shit! \N You shot me twice, you fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.31,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Quit moving around! \N I'm gonna aim for real this time, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.69,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Why did I just say such a stupid one-liner? {Hey, don't insult my editing you fucking jerk ;_; -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.56,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.86,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,What I should be asking is how the hell he's still alive! \N He took a bullet straight to the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.03,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Did my bullet somehow miss \N a vital part of his brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:33.95,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,That's real fucking cute, Mista.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.96,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Your name {\i1}is{\i0} Mista, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:43.29,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,I know you have a friend with you \N here in Capri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.92,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...but you're the only one \N who's seen my face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.26,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Eh, Mista?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:58.43,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,I got hit twice during your surprise attack \N after getting caught in your little trap with the radio, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:03.27,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...if I fight you one-on-one \N with my Stand, Kraftwerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:07.69,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...I'll have no problem deflecting the bullets \N from that puny revolver of yours. {This is referenced again in line 120.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:12.03,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,By the way, \N I was a little too distracted to count...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.66,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...but how many bullets have you shot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.62,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,You've fired four on the truck so far, \N haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.67,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,And I'm pretty sure you fired two \N back at the watchhouse in Marina Grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.01,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Am I right? \N Did I count that right, Mista? {At least Sale is better at math than Narancia. -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:37.39,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,So now I can get up close and personal \N and beat the crap out of you without worrying, right? {Retranslatorinated. Needs re-editinating. Previous edit had him saying that IF he got up close he wouldn't need to worry, but what he's actually saying is that he's safe TO get up close because Mista is out of bullets and can't stop him. -Starfish}{So now I can get up close and personal and beat the crap out of you... - suggestion from Jules}
