Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.52,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.19,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Th-This can't be happening! \N My left hand is stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.78,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.53,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey, you! \N How long you gonna keep driving forward?! Stop, you idiot! {Retranslated because "Quit driving and stop" felt redundant and also because the two are separate sentences in the Japanese. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.37,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I wish I could... \N Someone stop us, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.83,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Someone stop the truck! \N Nothing I do is working...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.46,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Think about it for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:05.88,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Why would I be so kind as to \N tell you that you're out of bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.80,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,You think I'm trying to help you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.26,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:13.26,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,The only reason I told you is because \N I'm confident you'll never escape this truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.64,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,Also, the driver can't take his foot \N off the gas pedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.10,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,...or let go of the steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:25.44,Main,Sale,0,0,0,,I'm telling you this because I know you can't reload \N with your left hand fixed to the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.41,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Those are the bullets \N that bastard's Stand deflected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:39.79,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,They're frozen there in midair, \N like he fixed them in place so they'd move with the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.25,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,Fixed in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:48.09,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He must have used his ability to fix the bullets in place midair, \N just like he fixed me and the driver to the truck...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:53.13,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,He has the ability to fix \N anything he touches in place! {But Mista is fixed in place and he didn't touch Mista, did he? TLC, mind double checking this? -Gyro}{Hyperliteral is "His ability is the ability to lock the things he touches in their place." So... This is just an error in the show itself if anything. -TLC}
